    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家在“漫游奇境”的过程中需要收集黄金轮轮来修复大电梯，解锁新的世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/021af4b2c1a3b1fa11280e81c0e87a2e.poster.avif?t=1737564431\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/021af4b2c1a3b1fa11280e81c0e87a2e.webm?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/021af4b2c1a3b1fa11280e81c0e87a2e.mp4?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以通过形形色色的冒险来达成这一目的，例如解谜、竞速、与可爱的角色互动，运用高超的移动技巧来收集散落各处的秘密。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/1404ef2f3135df32ce6b87a60bc9e4d8.poster.avif?t=1737564431\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/1404ef2f3135df32ce6b87a60bc9e4d8.webm?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/1404ef2f3135df32ce6b87a60bc9e4d8.mp4?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是喜欢推敲谜题、精确跳跃还是漫游观景，总有趣事在转角处等待着您。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/f0860cd8876da4e30662bbd5316b5391.poster.avif?t=1737564431\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/f0860cd8876da4e30662bbd5316b5391.webm?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/f0860cd8876da4e30662bbd5316b5391.mp4?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充分利用身边物体的属性：向下丢物体可以二段跳，抓着小鸡可以空中滑翔，用火箭达到疯狂极速……诸多内容等您尝试！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/f68d19f86e7d317b793c83d11c57abb3.avif?t=1737564431\" width=600 height=175 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您无需收集全部轮轮也可一路推进，所以跟着直觉来做最有趣的事情也未尝不可。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >惊心动魄的平台跳跃？丰富多彩的角色互动？亦或是面对地牢中的强大BOSS？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/3dc91e64c8d76a09a3c64fb40111d746.avif?t=1737564431\" width=600 height=175 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论您是完美主义者、休闲玩家、速通高手还是全收集爱好者，都能找到自己喜爱的方式通关！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
